org.eclipse.modisco.omg.smm
Interface SmmPackage

public interface SmmPackage

The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type

See Also:
SmmFactory

kind="package"
